Event Description:
Come one, come all
To the grandest carnival of em’ all!
After a brilliant debut season, Zomaland, India’s grandest food & entertainment carnival, is back for Season two!

With stunning attractions making every corner picturesque, incredible entertainment that set an electrifying vibe, world class chefs & mixologists, and above all, great food curated into multiple cuisine-based zones, all under one roof - Zomaland 2.0 will be bigger, grander & better! It will be the most magnificent showcase of food, music, art, comedy & games the country has ever seen!
Come on down to the grandest carnival in town to sample delicacies from the best eateries across the city, and get into the festive spirit as some of the best entertainers hit the stage to make you laugh, sway, groove and be amazed!
Think music, entertainment, games - Zomaland will have it all. Replete with food for every palate, games for all age groups, music for all ears and incredible attractions to please every eye (and camera, of course!), it's a spectacle that you’re not going to want to miss.

Here’s a little bit more about what Zomaland has in-store -
Great Food & Countless CuisinesFrom sushi to salad,There will be food for every palate!
Stunning AttractionsWith larger than life attractions all through,There will be plenty of photo opportunities for you!
Incredible EntertainmentThey've got music that’ll make you sing and sway,And performances that’ll light up your day!
And much much more!
Address: 84/36, N Main Rd, Koregaon Park Annexe, Mundhwa, Pune, Maharashtra 411001

One great weekend, a lifetime of memories.​

Event Name: Supermoon ft. Prateek Kuhad Winter Tour 2019 - Pune
Event Description:
Abhi toh Pune show baaki hai...aur Raat Raazi hai!
Here's some good news for all you Prateek Kuhad fans - Now you can get 3 tickets for the price of 2

After taking over the comedy scene, Zee Live's Supermoon is ready for Music!

Hosting the India leg of Prateek Kuhad's Winter Tour, Supermoon is all saddled up to venture into the world of music. Are you excited yet?
  
Prateek Kuhad’s Winter Tour is going to be his most ambitious one till date. He will be performing 30 shows across 8 countries, including USA, Canada, UK, France, Germany, Belgium, The Netherlands, Spain and India, where he will be starting and ending the tour across 11 cities.

Watch him Live at his Winter Tour with Zee Live’s Supermoon and see him work his magic.

Book your tickets on PayTM Insider

About Supermoon
Supermoon is an Intellectual Property of ZEE LIVE, a division of ZEE Entertainment Enterprises Limited (ZEEL), that has been curated with an objective of bringing the leading international entertainment acts from comedy, music, theatre, etc. to India. Supermoon is a phenomenon which aims to give Indian audiences an experience which is enriching and fulfilling to the soul.

About Prateek Kuhad
Hailed by Rolling Stone India as “one of the country’s leading singer-songwriters,” Prateek Kuhad has taken the rest of the world by storm in recent years, garnering a slew of accolades and honors around the globe with his mesmerizing, cinematic songwriting.

Since the release of his EP cold/mess in 2018, Prateek has extensively toured in support of the release. From selling out two tours in the US to playing across colleges and festivals in India, Prateek has become a certifiable success, while becoming one of the top streamed artists on Spotify when they launched in India.
Address: 84/36, N Main Rd, Koregaon Park Annexe, Mundhwa, Pune, Maharashtra 411001

Event Name: Prashasti Singh and Samay Raina - Live in Pune!
Event Description: See one of country's top comic, supported by a rising star who has recently brought comedy club audiences to its collective knees. Catch Prashasti Singh and Samay Raina - Live in Pune!About the Artists-Prashasti Singh - Prashasti Singh is a stand-up comic, writer, actor and improviser, who you've most recently seen in Amazon Prime Video's Comicstaan. She has been active in the Mumbai comedy circuit since 2015. She has 3 years of experience in improv comedy and 2 years in stand-up, performing across venues like Canvas Laugh Club, NCPA and the Cuckoo Club. Prior to comedy she has dabbled with theater and has performed at venues like Kamani auditorium in Delhi and Rangamandira in Bangalore. Prashasti has a degree in engineering from Delhi university and MBA from IIM Lucknow. She has worked with a Television Broadcast company for 4 years understanding and creating content for the heartland consumer.Modesty is clearly not her forte.Samay Raina - Samay Raina is a very secular Kashmiri Pandit born in Jammu, living in Pune having studied in Hyderabad after moving from Delhi. He is hilarious and his idiosyncratic style of delivery makes him even funnier.
Address: Kogobo Resto Bar & Banquet Baner, 4th Floor, The Mint, Opp. Kapil Malhar Society, Aundh - Baner Link Road, Riviresa Society, Baner, Pune, Maharashtra 411045

Event Name: Mentalism Special by Suhani Shah: Pune
Event Description: Suhani Shah is one of the biggest name in Indian magic today. With wonderful skills in sleight of hand, mind reading, situational comedy and audience participation, she brings audiences to their feet. Having started at such an early age, Suhani has experience beyond her years. Her stylish, sophisticated and charismatic persona contains a generous dose of wit, intelligence and humour. Her unique performance style and off-beat approach to her art has won the hearts of millions across the globe.Being a magician and a professional hypnotherapist, Suhani Shah understands the way people think, behave and react in certain conditions. She has combined her learning of human behaviour and psychological techniques with the art of magic to create her whole new magic soiree where she reads peoples thoughts and carry out other feats which can broadly be referred to as mentalism.
Address: Mulik Capital, Kalyani Nagar, Pune, Maharashtra 411014
